{
  "stem": "26699.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And like me, there were many others who hid their social origin, in order to be able to study.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the last year of university, the Communist pressure became unbearable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They started to check the validity of the curriculum vitae of all the students, to see if they told the truth or not.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in our hearts, we were frightened that they may discover that some of us lied.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They didn't find that I lied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They didn't have a proof.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But they found that one of our colleagues, through he was denounced by somebody else, by sort of a collaborator, a Communist collaborator, that his father owned cafeteria.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He declared that the father was an employee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But actually, he was a partner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was like a bakery, producing cakes and this sort of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Immediately, a big meeting with the 200 students of our year was organized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And denunciation speeches were given.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were asked to expel our colleague.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was put for an open vote.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And with the exceptional of a few, nobody voted for this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "This was a slap in the face of the local Communist boss.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Immediately, they organized a better meeting where they took people and they started to blackmail, in order to vote.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was one of the top students in that year.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they asked me to vote against this colleague of mine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And if not-- this was just a couple of days before graduation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Normally, the top students were taken as staff at the university.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And if I would not vote, not only that I would not get in the university as a lecturer or assistant, but I won't get a job any close to my town.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the same blackmail went to most of the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
